<content type="application/x.deki0805+xml" title="treerow"><body xmlns:eval="http://mindtouch.com/2007/dekiscript">
<div class="noinclude"><span class="script">XULRefElem()</span></div>
<p>A single row in a <span class="script">XULElem("tree")</span>. It should be placed inside a <span class="script">XULElem("treeitem")</span> element. Children of the <code>treerow</code> should be <span class="script">XULElem("treecell")</span> elements. If child rows are necessary, they should be placed in a <span class="script">XULElem("treechildren")</span> element inside the parent <span class="script">XULElem("treeitem")</span>.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Trees" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Trees">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
